This piece is hand made by craftsmen following smart design techniques in shop in Brooklyn, New York, minimizing waste by efficient use of resources, therefore passing the manufacturer direct savings to you.
description.647: The collection is crafted from pine solids and cherry veneers. Brighten up your bedroom with the simplistic style of this bedroom collection.
description.648: A practical piece for the home, Abner Contemporary Nightstand works a double shift as a living room accent table. Whether you wish to use this sophisticated classic as a bedside table or coffee table (or both!), you will revel in its chic 3-drawer design. Both solid rubber wood and engineered wood are used by Malaysian craftsmen for the designer nightstand's frame before finishing it with a very dark brown wood veneer. Maintain the modern end table's beauty by wiping its surfaces clean with a dry cloth as needed.
description.651: Awaken your bedroom with the traditional elegance of the Cortina bedside chest in honey walnut. It is built with exceptional craftsmanship and materials to bring high quality and enduring comfort. Create an atmosphere of relaxation in your bedroom with this magnificent piece.
description.652: Elegant solid wood and marble traditional style bedroom.
description.653: A perfect piece to place by your bedside, the International Concepts Unfinished 1 Drawer Nightstand is simple, graceful and minimally designed. Engineered out of solid parawood, this nightstand flaunts immaculate lines, which are quintessential of the contemporary style. It has an unfinished surface, which not only looks natural, but beautifully blends with most kind of color schemes and settings. It features one wide shelf at the bottom, and one box drawer at the top, which can be used to store anything from bedtime essentials to handy accessories. The Unfinished 1 Drawer Nightstand by International Concepts requires minimal assembly on arrival and can be put together without much hassle.
description.656: College Woodwork cases are constructed using solid birch and beech. Drawers boost heavy grade solid steel full extension glides. Buy with the confidence that you will enjoy your furniture for a lifetime.
description.657: Simplistic and functional, this Hokku Designs Alpha 2 Drawer Nightstand perfectly combines both design and utility in a marvelous way. The block feet design of the nightstand makes it sturdy and stable. This Alpha 2 Drawer Nightstand from Hokku Designs is made from wood and is varnished with a brown finish. The finger pull design of the handle of the drawers lends this modern nightstand a unique appeal. The drawer glides have a full extension capacity with safety stops which makes it safe to use. It can be dusted with a dry cloth from time to time and can be cleaned with mild cleaners if required.
description.658: The City Center Collection from HGTV Home is a casual urban look that has clean classic lines and is finished in a distinctive textured Ash Veneer.
description.659: Enhance your casual lifestyle with the minimalist look and unique design details of the Natural Elements Pier Nightstand. It is solidly constructed using environmentally friendly plantation hardwoods and knotty oak veneers. Complemented by the soft driftwood finish, the Natural Elements Pier Nightstand features 4 drawers for spacious storage with the ability to nest with the Dresser, Chest or Entertainment center for additional storage and a great look. Precise nesting is assured by the placement of levelers to keep the items seamlessly aligned. The full extension drawers feature English dovetail joints, drawers for maximum storage and roller ball bearing side guides to ensure smooth functioning. Bottom drawers feature dust proofing for added protection.
description.661: Tribecca mixes it up with modern, Art Deco, and Asian influences. Lighter scaled, with classic clean lines and pared down forms, Tribecca's inviting textures, rich wood tones and nickel finish hardware could be just the fresh look you've been trying to imagine for the new retirement condo on the shore or a trendy city loft.         This nightstand, with its 2 drawers and storage space, will be sure to provide you with all you need in a nightstand: convenience, storage space, and style.
description.662: Simple yet classy, the Vaughan-Bassett Hamilton Franklin 2 Drawer Nightstand is a great piece to setup with your bed. Perfect to hold a night lamp and bedtime essentials, this nightstand is made with a combination of veneer and hardwood solids for optimum durability. It is available in a range of beautiful finishes, which complement with most color schemes and settings. Contemporarily styled, the Vaughan-Bassett Hamilton Nightstand has two drawers, which can be used to store your small knick-knacks, books, or handy utilities. Easy to maintain and clean, this nightstand requires an occasional wipe with a dry cloth to remain dust-free.
description.666: Sleek and stylish, this unique DG Casa Hamilton 2 Drawer Nightstand has a modern and enigmatic appeal. The contemporary inspired frame of the nightstand has a neat design and ensures that the nightstand is sturdy and durable. This Hamilton 2 Drawer Nightstand from DG Casa is constructed from premium quality wood. This nightstand has a warm and affectionate brown finish that seamlessly blends in with a variety of decor settings. The simple knob design of the drawer’s handles has a royal gold finish that lends the nightstand with an imperial air. It is fully upholstered in long-lasting and easy to maintain synthetic leather.
description.667: Creatively inspired by the rich heritage of the City of Valencia, known as the 'Vienna of Spain', the Villa Valencia Bedside chest in Classic chestnut is beautifully constructed by skilled craftsmen and artisans from birch solids, cherry, pecan veneers and elm burl. Its carved accents will create a unique ambience for your home.
description.669: The Pacifica Nightstand is constructed of solid New Zealand Radiata wood with a rich espresso finish. With subtle raised panel detailing and its clean lines, the Pacifica Nightstand is simple yet elegant, handsome and stylish.
description.670: Made with select okoume veneer and hardwood solids. Case and bed feature heavy framed details in a dry vintage black color. Thick case top. English dovetail drawer boxes wrapped in light wood patterned paper wrapped have metal center guide. Cast binpull has a bronze color finish.
description.671: Bring home this traditional Wildon Home Montgomery 2 Drawer Nightstand and add a unique appeal to your bedroom decor. This nightstand has multiple drawers which offer sufficient space to store a variety of valuables. The drawers have a simple knob handle design which adds to their splendor. This Montgomery 2 Drawer Nightstand from Wildon Home is made from solid hardwood and veneer which makes it long-lasting. The nightstand is polished with a brown cappuccino finish that adds to its warm allure. This nightstand is made of non toxic materials which make it safe to use in homes especially where children reside.
description.672: Blissful simplicity is what the Tribeca collection features. It boasts crisp, clean lines and a rich wood grain high gloss finish.
description.673: Oversized casegoods for maximum storage capacity with deep drawers
description.674: Made with select veneers, Ash swirl accents and hardwood solids. Dark brown, gently distressed finish. Dark bronze color hardware. False bottom in night stand drawer for secret storage. French/English dovetail drawer interiors with color finish. Three piece ball bearing glide.
description.675: Taking the expected design elements of hard contemporary and putting a decidedly feminine curve into the mix makes the Lyric collection a unique addition to your new bedroom design.
description.677: Step into a comfortable surrounding that is Americana. Rustic design elements are apparent in the strong lines of the shaped, carved design and hand-applied antiqued black rubbed through finish providing an aged worn look. Constructed of mahogany solids with oak veneers and engineered wood. The Americana Night Stand features a physically distressed oak finished top featuring worm holes, fly specking, and small indentations. Other features include a shaped top with beveled edges, one storage drawer, and one lower shelf. Beautifully accented with brushed nickel hardware. Finish and measurements may vary slightly.
description.679: The Barcelona collection finished in a high gloss lacquer will add the perfect style complement to your bedroom.
description.680: Revamp your decor with this Najarian Furniture Key West 2 Drawer Nightstand. It is the perfect blend of style and functionality. The two drawers have dovetail joinery for structural integrity and are felt-lined for providing a soft surface. This Key West 2 Drawer Nightstand from Najarian Furniture is made from wood and is burnished with a pecan finish. The drawer glides have a full extension capacity with safety stops to ensure that it does not fall out. The drawer handles offer a firm grip. This Nightstand is CPSIA compliant and can be wiped clean with a soft, dry cloth to ensure that it looks as good as new for years to come.
description.681: Designed with the bedside in mind, nightstand brings all the best of the British Colonial collection together in one perfectly-sized piece. The projecting frieze on the top adds dimension, while the knobs, with their tarnished brass patina, add Old World charm. The final touch is the fully-turned bun feet, which uplift and lighten the overall appearance.
description.682: Elegant and versatile, the Wayborn Eiffel 2 Drawer Nightstand is an excellent option to keep by your bedside. Alternately, it can also be used as a console table due to its broad width of 29.5". Engineered out of Birchwood, it has a sturdy body that is designed to stand the test of time. The Wayborn Eiffel 2 Drawer Nightstand has a crisscross motif on its side panels, which is not only attractive, but also keeps everything on the shelves in its place. Quintessentially traditional, this nightstand displays a glossy brown finish that complements all kinds of color schemes and settings. The two mortise and tenon drawers on this nightstand have a 0.75 glide extension and safety stops, which can be used to store handy utilities or small knick-knacks.
description.683: The Alpine Furniture Urban 2 Drawer Nightstand is the perfect solution to storing miscellaneous items at a hands distance from your bedside. Crafted out of wood, this drawer nightstand has a sturdy structure and is durable. It is part of the Urban collection and has a merlot finish that accentuates its neat design and blends well with the interiors. The Urban 2 Drawer Nightstand by Alpine Furniture has two comfortably sized drawers, giving you sufficient storage space. The ball bearing glides and safety stops help the drawers to open and shut smoothly. Easy to care for, this drawer nightstand can be wiped with a clean damp cloth.
description.684: One of the first rustic furniture pieces designed and built by Montana Woodworks®, this nightstand design has more than proven it's ability to stand the test of time. The simple, yet durable nightstand will bring rustic elegance to any room of your home. Handcrafted of solid lodge pole pine by artisans, this highly useful accent table is just the right way to make a statement. Next to your log bed or as an end table in your home or office, you simply cannot go wrong. 20-years limited warranty included at no additional charge.
description.685: The Pathways collection offers timeless style in a comfortable, coastal design. The nightstand offers two storage drawers to keep your nighttime items close. Felt lining in the top drawer ensures your treasured items are protected from snags and scrapes. Decorative turned bun feet and antique gunmetal knobs with a rusty patina finish add to the charm of this nightstand.
description.688: This nightstand offers two medium drawers for storing smaller garments, scarves, fashion accessories, or even some light reading material - and an open shelf for your alarm clock, cell phone, or whatever you would like to store for easy access, just the perfect amount of space and size for a complimentary bed-side piece.
description.691: Ideally suited for smaller spaces, the Telephone Table is a nod to an era before cell phones, but a design that still holds an immense amount of function. Blending a more traditional air in an efficient form, the four drawers of the Table are elevated by the sturdy, spherical bun feet. A final element of style, the subtle metal knobs adorn without distracting, due to their understated decorative detailing.
description.692: The City Center Collection from HGTV Home is a casual urban look that has clean classic lines and is finished in a distinctive textured Ash Veneer.
description.693: The embodiment of elegance, the Colonial Classics collection by Home Styles provides a sophisticated retreat.
description.695: HGTV Home Furniture's newest collection, Voyage, brings together a casual styling with a Modern edge. Clean lines and generous scale combined with fashionable design details showcase this collection. Storage, versatility and function are key elements in the Bedroom, Dining, Occasional, and Entertainment pieces of this collection. A clean concave bar-pull hardware speaks to the modern edge, yet with its soft rolled texture and burnished rose gold finish, it creates an easy-to-live-with casual style.
description.696: Contemporary blonde nightstand with blonde vine motif.
description.698: Modern white finish. Blocky details throughout this generously scaled piece. Contemporary satin nickel color knobs. Swooping shaped base rail. Side roller glides for smooth operating drawers.
description.700: The three drawer night stand provides ample storage and features a planked top, fluted three quarter turn pilaster sides, heavy step molding at the top and bottom of the base, with a row of dentils molding running along the top of the base and four bun feet. The three drawers are graduated in size from smaller to larger, top to bottom.
description.702: From Montana Woodworks, the largest manufacturer of handcrafted quality log furnishings in America comes the all new Homestead collection line of furniture products. This nightstand with shelf is ideally suited next to the bed or can be used in living areas, waiting rooms and home offices.
description.704: Uniquely designed with leather all around the headboard, frame, and foot board , the dream bed elegantly harmonizes with decors of all different styles and colors. the exclusive design of the dream bed is sure to give a timeless appeal.
description.706: Neo-Rustic Distressed Acacia Veneer with a Gorgeous light gray finish aptly complements this Gorgeous Coastal and Plantation inspired shutter nigh stand. Full extension glides and door storage adds versatility and utility to this Timeless Complement to the Eden Bed.
description.707: Add a unique accent piece to your home decor with this dragon storage curio cabinet, entirely hand-carved from wood by talented artisans of northern Thailand. With its convenient storage spaces and richly polished top, this cabinet is an attractive storage solution for your hallway, living room, bedroom or anywhere else you can imagine. Each door features highly detailed dragons flying through the floral-filled sky, symbolizing the source of all energy and guarding over your precious possessions. Featuring a spacious pull-out drawer above two intricately carved doors, this acacia wood cabinet is the perfect complement to your home interior. The intricately detailed carvings and fine finish are a testament to the artisan's expert craftsmanship. This piece is handcrafted from the highest quality wood by artisans in the village of Baan Thawai, located in the historical Golden Triangle region of northern Thailand. EXP brings you authentic, handcrafted goods from a variety of world cultures. With this purchase you are not only receiving a beautiful product, but you are supporting the artisans and helping them to pursue their craft. This not only ensures the artistic development and financial stability of the talented individuals making these fine products, but also helps to preserve their rich cultural heritage of fine craftsmanship. The handcrafted nature of this product will produce minor differences in design and sizing. Subtle variations will occur from piece to piece, adding to the unique quality of individual items. Measurements may vary slightly.
description.708: Beside the bed or a chair, Telephone Table offers a generously sized top and ample storage space. Four drawers are crafted from cedar for an aromatic touch. Bun feet serve to lengthen and lighten the look of the Telephone Table. Finally, the use of English paste wax over the finish, creates a rich shine and smoothness to the overall design that beautifully plays into the timeless, traditional appeal.
description.711: Add an aura of elegance and sophistication to your decor with this angelo:HOME Marlowe 2 Drawer Nightstand. The nightstand has two drawers that offer sufficient storage space along with built-in power outlets for convenient charging of gadgets. This Marlowe 2 Drawer Nightstand from angelo:HOME is made from wood and is burnished with a chocolate brown finish. The drawers have a ball bearing glide that offers them a smooth open and closing mechanism. The finger pull design of the drawer handles provides an easy and firm grip. The nightstand can be wiped with a dry cloth from time to time.
description.712: Traditional country styling is perfectly presented with the Carollen collection. With a rub-through black finish that reveals hints of cherry below, each piece tells the tale of your personal aesthetic. Plank style paneling further lends to the country feel. The bow-fronted case pieces are punctuated with metal knob hardware in an antique brass finish.
description.713: Dark brown finish with replicated oak grain. Glossy faux marble tops and pilasters accented with satin nickel color flutes. Curved faux marble rope crowns and moulding use 3D press technology for an infinity edge. Satin nickel color bail handles with rope twist detail. Side roller glides for smooth operating drawers.
description.715: The distinct lines between contemporary and transitional styling have been blended to create the Arcola. Highlighted by an espresso finish, embossed wood panels, with drifted dark oak finish, are utilized as a contrast to the clean contemporary feel. Wood knob drawer pulls further accent the case piece.
description.716: This nightstand features two fully sanded and finished snag free interior drawers with metal glides. The top is removable if desired.
description.717: Replicated almost black paint with a merlot color undercoat. Blocky details throughout this generously scaled piece. Side roller glides for smooth operating drawers. Contemporary satin nickel color knobs. Swooping shaped base rail.
description.718: Timeless style is captured in the transitional Verity collection. Metal drawer knobs are featured in an antiqued bronze, which complements the cherry finish perfectly. With design elements that make this bedroom suite a perfect choice in a number of home decors, the Verity collection will be a perfect fit for your newly decorated sanctuary.
description.721: Elegant solid wood and marble traditional style bedroom.
description.722: Ash swirl and birch veneers with Asian hardwoods. Plywood drawer box construction with English/English dovetails. Full extension ball bearing side guides and fully finished drawer interiors. Traditional dark cherry stain finish. Serpentine shaped dresser design with natural marble parquetry top. Elaborately moulded ornamentation throughout.
description.723: Versatile and modern all wood nightstand with a drawer and a shelf.
description.724: This night stand is slightly smaller in scale, but still offers plenty of style. Like the larger pieces in the collection, this piece features serpentine shaped top, octagonal posts, and the entire drawer front echoes the signature scalloped shape. The top drawer is felt lined.
description.725: Preston Ridge is rooted in classic forms with exciting updates for today's generation. The collection's 18th Century roots get a dash of pizzazz through dramatic shape and curves and a rich two-tone finish combining cherry veneers with a sophisticated black rub-through finish and gold tone accenting. Preston Ridge offers updated traditional styling with the sophistication of finely crafted Old World antiques.
description.729: Make a stylish statement with this Global Furniture USA New York 2 Drawer Nightstand. The contemporary design of this rounded nightstand makes it safe to use in homes with children. This New York 2 Drawer Nightstand from Global Furniture USA is made from high quality wood and it has a glossy finish. The two spacious drawers have a simple knob handle design which has a sterling silver finish. The glass top of the nightstand can be used as a decorative space to place amusing lampshades, remote controls, or telephones.
description.730: This collection has a unique crocodile pattern combined with rhinestone "bling" hardware and mirror trims. The extra tall headboard set the tone for this luxe look in an all black finish. Drawers offer plenty of storage space with extension glides. This bedroom collection was made for those who enjoy the exotic look.
description.731: This ultra modern 2 drawers nightstand is fitted with full extension metal glides, English dovetail construction and a top felt-lined drawer.
description.732: The Louis Phillip Bedroom obviously draws its inspirations from the timeless designs of the 18th century France. The use of solid hardwoods and select veneers make this furniture durable and long lasting, while the sumptuous brown cherry finish gives the depth, clarity and beauty to the wood. Dove-tail drawer construction and attention to quality combines the contemporary functionality with just the right amount of tradition.
description.735: Pastoral elegance is the hallmark of Hillsdale's Pine Island bedroom collection. The Pine Island nightstand, authentic in both style and substance, is an upright piece featuring two generously scaled drawers ideal for next-to-the-bed storage necessities. It is constructed of solid wood using pine solids and lumber sides.
description.736: The Glacier Country collection features a truly unique finish reminiscent of the Grand Lodges of the Rockies, circa 1900. Craftsmen remove the outer bark using old-fashioned draw knives while leaving the inner cambium layer intact for increased texture and contrast. The process is completed in a professional eight step process that applies stain and lacquer for a durable, low maintenance finish. Dark, rich hues and tones provide an extraordinary appearance! One of the first rustic furniture pieces designed and built by Montana Woodworks, this nightstand design has more than proven its ability to stand the test of time. The simple, yet durable, nightstand will bring rustic elegance to any room of your home. Handcrafted of solid lodge pole pine by our artisans, this highly useful accent table is just the right way to make a statement. Next to your log bed or as an end table in your home or office, you simply cannot go wrong.
description.740: The elegant and functional design of the Jaxson bedroom collection will be a wonderful addition to any bedroom in your home. The piece features bevelled drawer fronts and felt lining. Finished in an atrractive cappuccino, choose this set for a warm and tranquilizing look in your home.
description.741: With an air of urban sophistication, the Edmonston will be a bold statement in your newly decorated bedroom. The bold oval ring hardware is an intense contrast to rich espresso finish. Concave accents punctuate the design and lend to the contemporary aesthetic.
description.742: This traditional piece is sleekly designed with a warm light natural oak finish, and for the money this nightstand is a great buy. If you're looking for style without the high price of most furniture stores this nightstand will be a great addition to any room setting.
description.743: Add a touch of transitional charm to your bedside with this beautiful night stand. It features two spacious drawers and a lovely finish. Place it alongside your bed with a lamp or a photo on top for a brilliant bedroom accent piece.
description.745: One drawer with beveled interior sits below an open compartment with glass insert above. The hand painted gold accents throughout is complimented by custom designed hardware pulls and ferrules are finished in a rose-gold. Finish is a very elegant cathedral walnut.
description.746: The influence of French Regal comes to life with this unique collection. A classic French look with a chic twist depicting a hip, couture feel. Traditional carvings are highlighted with a glazed silver metallic tipping.
description.747: This handcrafted nightstand with drawer exemplifies just the right balance between aesthetics and utility.
description.748: ARTLESS THN pieces expand the minimalist language we find at the heart of our designs. This new and expanding collection is the unintended marriage between two ARTLESS lines. The solid Walnut of the SQ Family and the contrasting lacquered elements of the Units. In the case of the THN, the solid Walnut becomes a protective box enveloping two smaller lacquered drawer boxes. The lacquered boxes are proportioned to be two thirds of the piece. With this move the functionality and mass of the drawers is exacerbated with the visual appeal of an open, see-through space.   THN stands for “The Hawks Nest” a name chosen by one of our earliest and greatest supporters, and a very dear client.
description.749: Made with select veneer and hardwood solids in a rustic brown finish. Saw distress effect detail on pilasters. Planked and chisel distress effect on case tops and panels. Framed doors on dresser and chest. Craftsman inspired hardware has oil rubbed bronze color finish. Sanded and sealed drawer boxes with ball bearing side guides. Twin bunk bed has saw distress effect detail on posts. Planked and chisel distress effect on case tops and panels. Bunk beds can be set up individually.
description.750: Handsome and edgy, this piece is practical and light hearted. They are the true conversation piece in your room. you can have fun and still keep it functional.
description.752: With an unexpected contrast that only serves to heighten the elegant profile, the Bayard Park will provide you the perfect opportunity to show off your personal style. Offered in a warm cherry finish and heavily carved in traditional style - featuring shell motif, distinctly curved legs and bombe shape.
description.753: The Lodge collection invites you to sit down, get comfortable and stay a while. Select alder and cottonwood are used to build functional and sturdy pieces for years to come. Casually elegant and striking, all the pieces in this collection display eye pleasing appeal, bringing you images of a quiet mountain country getaway; an escape from daily routine, in your own home
description.754: Sleek and stylish, this unique Hokku Designs Traxler 2 Drawer Nightstand has a modern and enigmatic appeal. The nightstand has two drawers which have an automatic self close drawer glide that adds to its utility. This Traxler 2 Drawer Nightstand from Hokku Designs is made from premium quality wood and is polished with a dark walnut finish. The finger pull design of the drawer handle enhances the design of the nightstand. The drawers have a cam and screw joinery design. The nightstand can be wiped clean with a soft dry cloth from time to time; strong liquid cleaners are not required.
description.755: The Beckett nightstand offers generous bedside storage with two different drawer depths.
description.756: Designers have made this chic looking night stand with excellent quality products. With stainless steel finish and self-closing mechanism.
description.757: Invite a warm welcome blend of traditional elegance with a hint of European influences, rich in tradition yet sophisticated in style, into your home. Take your bedroom to the next level of timeless appeal, stylish comfort and serenity for years to come!
description.758: Modern in design, a Wicker Park nightstand provides bedside practicality with urbane style. Drawers are equipped with full-extension drawer guides.
description.760: A style that bridges the gap from contemporary to transitional. The dark finish slightly highlighted on simple cherry veneers accentuates the design features of this collection.
description.761: Our Coal Harbor bedroom collection has an urban and sophisticated style making it ideal for contemporary, transitional and eclectic decor. The clean, unadorned appearance creates a feeling of simplicity and calmness.
description.762: Combining the clean, unadorned lines of the International Modernists with organic and geometric forms, the Catalina Collection is suggestive of the works of America's Mid-Century Modern designers.
description.765: Esoteric style nightstands combine grey and white color cues to blend seamlessly. The nightstands feature smooth operating self- closing drawers that will ensure years of flawless operation with minimal wear and tear.
description.766: Effortlessly plug in your radio, clock or music device with the night stand's wire management and cord access feature. This collection is made from poplar wood and cherry veneer finished in an impressive burnished cognac.
description.768: Dubbed "New York Revival," the new Regan collection updates contemporary boathouse style with a fresh, inky-black wink. One look and you're hooked, featuring a black painted finish with brushed nickel hardware.
description.769: Icon is distinguished by linear style, embellished by chromed inlay and legs.
description.770: Glamorous uptown design provides style to any home. Crystal accents, dynamic urban onyx finish, alluring jewel eye decorative hardware, clean tapered high leg styling.
description.771: Carved rosettes on the aptly named Rosette Bedside Table punctuate the three generous fixed shelves of this beautifully accommodating piece.
description.772: Loyally echoing the design details of the larger pieces, the bowed front and tapered legs make this nightstand a compact representation of key design elements of the Intrigue Collection. Step molding under the top, three drawers graduated in size and the carved collar detail at the top of the tapered legs, all complement the other bedroom pieces.
description.774: Add an elegant flair to your bedroom with this minimalistic Hokku Designs Zen 1 Drawer Nightstand. The block feet design of the nightstand lends it a sturdy and reliable quality. This nightstand has a single drawer which has a metal ball bearing drawer glide. The drawer has a nail and glue joinery design which lends it a smooth mechanism. It can be placed on the floor near the bed. The top of the nightstand is apt to place a jug of water or an alarm clock.
description.775: The Lorrenzia Nightstand is the perfect example of simplicity combined with functionality. Each drawer features extra supportive English dovetail construction and handy smooth and durable full-extension metal glides to accommodate plenty of belongings. Finished in a beautiful antique dark oak, this beautiful piece is perfect for any traditional home.
description.776: The District bedroom collection is inspired by the simplicity of urban design; the Two-Drawer Nightstand features bold brushed metal handles and a sleek facade. the washed black laminate fuses together classic black with warm brown undertones to create a high-end look. description.778: Casual cottage styling that can work from coast to coast. Mindy veneers combine with three different finishes that work together to create an eclectic feel for today's homes. Versatile pieces with charming details such as turned posts and linen accents.

description.782: The Axel nightstand's sturdy 'crate' shape and raw wood texture enhance its urban industrial style.

description.785: HGTV Home Furniture's newest collection, Voyage, brings together a casual styling with a Modern edge. Rich details such as rounded pilasters and bead molding accents, combined with mapa burl and hickory veneers, finished in a rich nutmeg with natural highlights in the grain pattern of the wood.
description.790: Dry vintage cream finish with replicated oak grain and authentic touch. Side roller glides for smooth operating drawers. Large scaled rustic pilasters. Slim profile dual USB charger located on the back of the night stand tops. Substantial warm pewter drawer handles.
description.791: The Cameron nightstand features a set of matching drawers.
description.792: Boasting an impressive medium oak finish, this handsome nightstand will make for a great addition to your bedroom. This impressive nightstand provides excellent storage solutions with its two drawers.

description.794: The classic design elements make the three drawer nightstand a versatile addition to any room.
description.796: Two drawer outwardly slanted blue mirror panel drawer faces. Slant allows for easy handling from underneath to open or close drawers on night table.
description.798: Store your medications and bedside necessities in the Nexera Nocce Truffle 2 Drawer Nightstand. description.982: Classic styling that works with any décor. Parkwood offers cherry veneers in a cognac finish accented by pewter drop bail hardware that ties nicely with the metal inserts in the headboard and mirror.
description.987: Traditionally designed, the Sunset Trading Cameron 3 Drawer Nightstand is an elegant option to keep by your bedside. Made out of manufactured wood, this nightstand is highly durable and sturdy. It has a rich cherry finish, which blends with all kinds of color schemes and settings. It features felt lined top drawers, which add a simple touch of sophistication to this nightstand. The Sunset Trading Cameron Nightstand has three spacious with safety stops, which can be used to store anything from handy utilities to small knick-knacks. Being non-toxic, this nightstand is viable in surroundings with children or pets. It has the General Conformity Certificate to ensure that the nightstand complies with all consumer-product safety rules.
description.989: This Arts and Crafts-inspired Hudson collection bed will compliment any bedroom. Clean, simple lines, this piece is built using solid wood and select veneers. This piece is hand made by craftsmen following smart design techniques in shop in Brooklyn, New York, minimizing waste by efficient use of resources, therefore passing the manufacturer direct savings to you.
description.990: Classic traditional with raised panel doors, solid drawer fronts and crown molding.
description.993: The fluid notes from a symphony come to life with Serenade by Klaussner Home. Serenade is a unique composition and harmony of fashion, style and design. The design takes sleek, contemporary forms and softens them with flowing, unexpected curves. Double serpentine shapes on case fronts create fluid movement in the collection.
description.994: Egerton's beautiful nightstand is a piece of furniture that hearkens back to the days of the European Renaissance. This lovely three drawer nightstand is the ideal piece to have next to a bed, couch or lounge chair. Plus, it has a convenient, sliding top that opens up to reveal a hidden storage area with a charging function for your electronics.
description.997: Enhancing the contemporary design of your bedroom is the focus of the Edina Collection. The espresso-hinted cherry finish builds on the unexaggerated lines of this bedroom suite, blended with the tufted bi-cast vinyl inserts on the headboard and the polished nickel hardware, culminates to achieve the modern look. Whether it is a hard contemporary or a softer transitional feel, your décor design options are wide open with this classic bedroom collection.
description.998: An attractive addition to your contemporary urban retreat, the Park Nightstand features a pristine steel base. Linen drawer linings and European soft-closing drawer glides enhance this two-drawer bedside table's significance as a sophisticated showpiece.
description.999: Bring back the island essence with the Cabana Banana Side Table by Home Styles. Constructed of 100% eco-friendly sustainable materials. Weave features hand-braided, four over two woven pattern banana leaves over plywood with mahogany solids in a cinnamon finish. Styled to create texture in any room such as entryway, living room, bedroom, etc. Finish and measurements may vary slightly.
description.1002: Allowing for flexible placement in a variety of home decors is the Nancy collection. Brushed nickel hardware accents each case piece. The merlot finish lends to the versatile look of the collection.
description.1005: You'll be set with this nightstand at your bedside. The piece carries a warm cherry brown finish and features pine solids as well as cherry veneers, a combination that evokes a sense of sophistication. In addition, the intricate carvings add just the right amount of thoughtful detail. Plus, the drawer and two doors are great for keeping books, magazines, pens and alarm clocks. With a wealth of elegance, this Bachelor's chest is sure to please.

Product Care:  This lacquer-based product is subject to be damaged by moisture, heat, or contact with alcohol-based and oil-based products. Never allow water or damp items to sit on your furniture including cleaning cloths, sponges, etc. Never allow alcohol-based products including some cleaners, nail polish and perfumes to come in contact with your wood furniture. They can dissolve the furniture finish on contact, requiring professional repairs. Do not allow plastic, including plastic or rubber placemats or rubberized feet on appliances, to come in direct contact with your furniture. Chemicals in the plastic may soften and injure the finish if exposed over a long period of time. Avoid direct sunlight, heat outlets, open windows, and dampness. Prolonged exposure to direct sunlight can fade the finish of your furniture, while extreme temperature and humidity changes can cause cracking or splitting. Dust frequently with a clean, damp lint-free cloth to remove abrasive buildup which can damage the finish over time. Occasionally polish with a high-quality non-silicone furniture polish every few months to enhance the beauty of the multi-step finish. Spray the polish onto a clean cotton cloth, apply it to the furniture, and then buff with a second clean, dry cotton cloth. Note that any polish may make a low sheen finish appear more glossy. Additionally, it is important to avoid oily polishes and waxes.

Product Care:  This lacquer-based product is subject to be damaged by moisture, heat, or contact with alcohol-based and oil-based products. Never allow water or damp items to sit on your furniture including cleaning cloths, sponges, etc. Never allow alcohol-based products including some cleaners, nail polish and perfumes to come in contact with your wood furniture. They can dissolve the furniture finish on contact, requiring professional repairs. Do not allow plastic, including plastic or rubber placemats or rubberized feet on appliances, to come in direct contact with your furniture. Chemicals in the plastic may soften and injure the finish if exposed over a long period of time. Avoid direct sunlight, heat outlets, open windows, and dampness. Prolonged exposure to direct sunlight can fade the finish of your furniture, while extreme temperature and humidity changes can cause cracking or splitting. Dust frequently with a clean, damp lint-free cloth to remove abrasive buildup which can damage the finish over time. Occasionally polish with a high-quality non-silicone furniture polish every few months to enhance the beauty of the multi-step finish. Spray the polish onto a clean cotton cloth, apply it to the furniture, and then buff with a second clean, dry cotton cloth. Note that any polish may make a low sheen finish appear more glossy. Additionally, it is important to avoid oily polishes and waxes.

867:
Features

Cedar is the natural choice because of its beauty, practicality and durability. Rustic Cedar uses only the finest cedar to create furniture that lasts for generations. It is naturally resistant to decay, insect and weather damage. Because of this superior resistance, cedar is frequently used for outdoor fencing, and siding on homes. Cedar has an exceptionally high strength-to-weight ratio, which means that it is both durable and easy to move about. It does not shrink or wrap as many other woods commonly do. Unlike pressure-treated wood furniture, Rustic Cedar uses no chemical preservatives that may be harmful to your family's health. 
All cedar log furniture is subject to the natural process of checking as the wood ''seasons.'' Checking occurs as wood releases moisture across or through the annual growth rings and it does not affect the structural performance or integrity of the wood. Therefore cracks in Cedar furniture are quite normal and can happen at any time. The cracks can vary in sizes but are sure to not affect the quality or resistance of the product as this is a natural process of Cedar furniture.

Product Care:  This lacquer-based product is subject to be damaged by moisture, heat, or contact with alcohol-based and oil-based products. Never allow water or damp items to sit on your furniture including cleaning cloths, sponges, etc. Never allow alcohol-based products including some cleaners, nail polish and perfumes to come in contact with your wood furniture. They can dissolve the furniture finish on contact, requiring professional repairs. Do not allow plastic, including plastic or rubber placemats or rubberized feet on appliances, to come in direct contact with your furniture. Chemicals in the plastic may soften and injure the finish if exposed over a long period of time. Avoid direct sunlight, heat outlets, open windows, and dampness. Prolonged exposure to direct sunlight can fade the finish of your furniture, while extreme temperature and humidity changes can cause cracking or splitting. Dust frequently with a clean, damp lint-free cloth to remove abrasive buildup which can damage the finish over time. Occasionally polish with a high-quality non-silicone furniture polish every few months to enhance the beauty of the multi-step finish. Spray the polish onto a clean cotton cloth, apply it to the furniture, and then buff with a second clean, dry cotton cloth. Note that any polish may make a low sheen finish appear more glossy. Additionally, it is important to avoid oily polishes and waxes.

Product Care:  This lacquer-based product is subject to be damaged by moisture, heat, or contact with alcohol-based and oil-based products. Never allow water or damp items to sit on your furniture including cleaning cloths, sponges, etc. Never allow alcohol-based products including some cleaners, nail polish and perfumes to come in contact with your wood furniture. They can dissolve the furniture finish on contact, requiring professional repairs. Do not allow plastic, including plastic or rubber placemats or rubberized feet on appliances, to come in direct contact with your furniture. Chemicals in the plastic may soften and injure the finish if exposed over a long period of time. Avoid direct sunlight, heat outlets, open windows, and dampness. Prolonged exposure to direct sunlight can fade the finish of your furniture, while extreme temperature and humidity changes can cause cracking or splitting. Dust frequently with a clean, damp lint-free cloth to remove abrasive buildup which can damage the finish over time. Occasionally polish with a high-quality non-silicone furniture polish every few months to enhance the beauty of the multi-step finish. Spray the polish onto a clean cotton cloth, apply it to the furniture, and then buff with a second clean, dry cotton cloth. Note that any polish may make a low sheen finish appear more glossy. Additionally, it is important to avoid oily polishes and waxes.
